[[釘鞋|釘鞋]]是[[運動鞋|運動鞋]]的一種，適用於[[賽跑|賽跑]]、[[足球|足球]]、[[棒球|棒球]]、[[高爾夫球具#球鞋|高爾夫]]等運動穿著，主要的優點耐磨、高回彈力。釘鞋釘的部分大多採用金屬、陶瓷或塑膠為材料製成，令鞋子的防滑性能提高，適合各種場地跑步選手使用。釘鞋起初於1860年代在英國流行<ref>{{cite book|title=A history of American amateur athletics and aquatics: with the records|last=Janssen|first=Frederick William|year=1888|oclc=38503721|publisher=Outing company|location=|isbn=|page=126|url=http://www.google.com/search?q=spike+shoe+running&hl=en&sa=X&ei=nFB2Tc6vEcmx0QH4xpHlBg&ved=0CDoQpwUoBA&source=lnt&tbs=bks%3A1%2Ccdr%3A1%2Ccd_min%3A1850%2Ccd_max%3A12%2F31%2F1900&tbm=#sclient=psy&hl=en&tbs=bks:1%2Ccdr%3A1%2Ccd_min%3A1%2F1%2F1850%2Ccd_max%3A1889&q=%22everybody+agreed+that+if+they+were+in+common+use+by+English+athletes%2C+they+must+be+desirable+for+Americans%22&aq=f&aqi=&aql=&oq=&pbx=1&bav=on.2,or.&fp=f6f1bcc041db8b52|accessdate=March 8, 2011|archive-date=2019-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701105049/https://www.google.com/search?q=spike%2Bshoe%2Brunning&hl=en&sa=X&ei=nFB2Tc6vEcmx0QH4xpHlBg&ved=0CDoQpwUoBA&source=lnt&tbs=bks%3A1%2Ccdr%3A1%2Ccd_min%3A1850%2Ccd_max%3A12%2F31%2F1900&tbm=&gws_rd=ssl#sclient=psy&hl=en&tbs=bks:1%2Ccdr%3A1%2Ccd_min%3A1%2F1%2F1850%2Ccd_max%3A1889&q=%22everybody+agreed+that+if+they+were+in+common+use+by+English+athletes%2C+they+must+be+desirable+for+Americans%22&aq=f&aqi=&aql=&oq=&pbx=1&bav=on.2,or.&fp=f6f1bcc041db8b52|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在鞋底加上釘子的概念可能源於更早的時間。

